## 🧠 Why I Built This
As someone with ADHD, I constantly struggled with:
- Forgetting medications ("Did I take my pills today?")
- Missing appointments (time blindness)
- Last-minute panic when arriving places
- "Out of sight, out of mind" tasks

This app solves those problems with **brain-friendly reminders**.

## ✨ Key Features
| Feature | How It Helps ADHD |
|---------|-------------------|
| 🔊 **Voice Alerts** | Auditory cues bypass working memory issues |
| 📍 **Location Triggers** | "Buy milk when near grocery store" reminders |
| 🕒 **Time-Based** | Visual countdowns for time blindness |
| 🆘 **Emergency Mode** | One-tap location sharing with caregivers |

## 🚀 Get Started in 30 Seconds
1. Open the [live app](https://ontime-guardian-pro.vercel.app)
2. Tap "+" to add a reminder
3. Choose:
   - ⏰ Time-based ("8AM meds")
   - 📍 Location-based ("When I leave work")
4. Get reminded **exactly when needed**

